graph TD
    USER_INPUT[User Input] --> ORCH[AgentOrchestrator.process]
    
    ORCH --> ATTEMPT{Attempt < max_retries?}
    
    ATTEMPT -->|Yes| RUN_GRAPH[Run Agent Graph]
    ATTEMPT -->|No| ERROR[ErrorEvent]
    
    RUN_GRAPH --> STREAM[Stream Messages]
    
    STREAM --> CHECK_MSG{Message Type?}
    
    CHECK_MSG -->|ToolMessage| PARSE_TOOL[Parse Tool Result]
    CHECK_MSG -->|AIMessage| COLLECT_TEXT[Collect Text]
    
    PARSE_TOOL --> COMPONENT{Has component_type?}
    COMPONENT -->|Yes| BUFFER[Buffer ComponentEvent]
    COMPONENT -->|No| CHECK_UI{Has ui_action?}
    CHECK_UI -->|Yes| UI_EVENT[UIActionEvent]
    CHECK_UI -->|No| CONTINUE[Continue]
    
    BUFFER --> YIELD_COMP[Yield ComponentEvent]
    UI_EVENT --> YIELD_UI[Yield UIActionEvent]
    COLLECT_TEXT --> YIELD_TEXT[Yield Text]
    
    YIELD_COMP --> SUCCESS[Success]
    YIELD_UI --> SUCCESS
    YIELD_TEXT --> SUCCESS
    
    RUN_GRAPH -->|Exception| CATCH_ERROR{Catch Error}
    
    CATCH_ERROR -->|LLMParseError| RETRY_LLM[Retry with Error Message]
    CATCH_ERROR -->|ToolExecutionError| CHECK_RETRY{should_retry?}
    CATCH_ERROR -->|AgentException| ERROR
    CATCH_ERROR -->|Other Exception| ERROR
    
    CHECK_RETRY -->|Yes| RETRY_TOOL[Retry with Error Message]
    CHECK_RETRY -->|No| ERROR
    
    RETRY_LLM --> ATTEMPT
    RETRY_TOOL --> ATTEMPT
    
    style USER_INPUT fill:#E6F3FF
    style ORCH fill:#FFE6CC
    style RUN_GRAPH fill:#D4EDDA
    style SUCCESS fill:#90EE90
    style ERROR fill:#FFB6C1
    style RETRY_LLM fill:#FFF4E6
    style RETRY_TOOL fill:#FFF4E6
